ent Awards to recognize UNT alumni and friends who are making an impact in their careers and the university In addition to signature awards events, UNT bestows President Awards — the highest university honors — to recognize UNT community members who go above and beyond to make the university, their communities, the region and the state better. Visit the award categories to learn more about university awards and how you can nominate a UNT community member to recognize their outstanding achievements. Visit Us Hurley Administration Bldg Mail Us University of North Texas 1155 Union Circle #311277 Denton, Texas 76203-5017 Contact Us 940-565-2108 urcm@unt.edu Technical issues? Site last updated on April 13, 2017 Disclaimer| AA/EOE/ADA| Privacy| Electronic Accessibility| State of Texas Online| Emergency Preparedness| THECB Online Resume System Student Consumer Information| UNT Compliance Hotline| Governors Committee on People with Disabilities| Texas Veterans Portal| UNT Home Site last updated on April 13, 2017 | Important Links 